                        center-to-limb-variation function
fun_clv_function        Calculates the standardized
                        center-to-limb-variation function
fun_clv_rmplane         Subtracts plane from image
fun_date2jd             Calculates Julian Date from a vector containing
                        date with time objects
fun_date_grid           Provides a tibble with dates from start to end
fun_deltaT              Calculates delta T in seconds according to
                        formulae by Fred Espenak
fun_disc_center         Calculates disc center coordinates and radius
                        of the indicator disc
fun_disc_coordinates    Determines heliografic coordinates
fun_disc_grid           Calculates grid of heliografic longitudes and
                        latitudes
fun_disc_math           Implements mathematical image manipulations.
fun_disc_rings          Assigns ring number to disc pixels
fun_extract_col         Extracts a single column of image frame
fun_extract_row         Extracts a single row of image frame
fun_flip_image          Flips the provided image
fun_flop_image          Flops the provided image
fun_gather_csv          Gathers output files of an index
fun_grid_plt            Adds grid to an image
fun_hdr2list            Extracts image header to list
fun_jd2date             Calculates date and time vector from Julian
                        Dates vector
fun_mask_border         Marks the border pixels of a given mask
fun_mask_circle         Determines a circle given the center
                        coordinates and the radius
fun_mask_create         Marks all pixels above or equal a given
                        threshold
fun_mask_diff           Marks all pixels between two given thresholds
fun_mask_fill           Fills out a given mask
fun_mat2tibbl           Umwandlung einer Matrix in ein tibble
fun_parse_header        Parses FITS header
fun_readFITSarray       Reads FITS binary array from disc
fun_read_header         Reads FITS ASCII header from disc
fun_read_image          Reads FITS image from disc
fun_ring_get            Returns ring parameters given a theta value
fun_ring_plt            Adds a ring to the image given a theta value
fun_sdo_keywords        Updates the header and hdrlst with sdo-specific
                        keywords
fun_sun_ephem           Calculates ephemeris for physical coordinates
                        of the Sun
fun_tibbl2mat           Umwandlung einer tibble oder eines data.frames
                        in eine Matrix
fun_write_header        Writes image header
fun_write_image         Writes FITS image to disc
mod_clv_correction      Fits the clv function, calibrate it and
                        flattens the image
